---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const tsSnippet = String.raw`npm install @chert/sdk

import { ChertClient } from '@chert/sdk';

const client = new ChertClient({
  endpoint: 'https://mainnet.chert.com',
  network: 'mainnet'
});`;

const rustSnippet = String.raw`[dependencies]
chert-sdk = "0.1.0"

use chert_sdk::{ChertClient, ClientConfig, Network};`;
---

<Layout title="SDKs - Silica Protocol" description="Official SDK coverage for the Silica ecosystem across TypeScript, Rust, Python, Go, and C#.">
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-950 text-white py-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(20,184,166,0.28) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(20,184,166,0.28) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-[360px] h-[360px] rounded-full bg-teal-500/15 blur-[120px] animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/4 w-[320px] h-[320px] rounded-full bg-green-500/15 blur-[120px] animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 6s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-teal-500/30 bg-teal-500/10 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-teal-300 mb-6">SDK coverage</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Build with <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-teal-400 to-green-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Silica client libraries</span></h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-teal-100/90 max-w-3xl mb-6">
          The repository currently includes SDK implementations for TypeScript, Rust, Python, Go, and C#. Many packages still use Chert naming in code and package registries while targeting the Silica protocol stack.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">SDK matrix</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Every SDK is aimed at the same core jobs: network queries, wallet flows, privacy operations, staking, and governance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-cyan-500/20 flex flex-col"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-cyan-300 mb-2">TypeScript</h3><p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mb-3">Package: <code class="text-cyan-300">@chert/sdk</code></p><p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-5 flex-1">Type-safe browser and Node integration with wallet, privacy, staking, and governance helpers.</p><a href="https://github.com/Silica-Protocol/sdk-typescript" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-300 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-cyan-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">GitHub repo</a></div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-orange-500/20 flex flex-col"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-orange-300 mb-2">Rust</h3><p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mb-3">Crate: <code class="text-orange-300">chert-sdk</code></p><p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-5 flex-1">Async-first Rust client for backend services, bots, validators, and tooling.</p><a href="https://github.com/Silica-Protocol/sdk-rust" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-300 border border-orange-500/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-orange-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">GitHub repo</a></div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-emerald-500/20 flex flex-col"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-emerald-300 mb-2">Python</h3><p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mb-3">Package: <code class="text-emerald-300">chert-sdk</code></p><p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-5 flex-1">Async Python client with type hints and pydantic-style validation ergonomics.</p><a href="https://github.com/Silica-Protocol/sdk-python" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-300 border border-emerald-500/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-emerald-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">GitHub repo</a></div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-sky-500/20 flex flex-col"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-sky-300 mb-2">Go</h3><p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mb-3">Module: <code class="text-sky-300">github.com/silica-network/chert/sdk/go</code></p><p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-5 flex-1">Concurrent Go client for services that need simple deployment and low runtime overhead.</p><a href="https://github.com/Silica-Protocol/sdk-go" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-300 border border-sky-500/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-sky-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">GitHub repo</a></div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-purple-500/20 flex flex-col"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-300 mb-2">C#</h3><p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mb-3">Package: <code class="text-purple-300">Chert.Sdk</code></p><p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-5 flex-1">.NET-friendly async client with strong typing and DI-ready patterns.</p><a href="https://github.com/Silica-Protocol/sdk-csharp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-300 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-purple-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">GitHub repo</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-950">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-teal-500/20">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between gap-6">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Source lives in individual repositories</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 max-w-3xl">These SDKs are not abstract placeholders on the site — each one already has its own GitHub repository under <code class="text-teal-300">Silica-Protocol/*</code>, so developers can jump straight from the overview page to the implementation, README, examples, and issue tracker.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://github.com/Silica-Protocol" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-green-500 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-teal-500/30 transition-all duration-300">Open SDK org</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-950">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-cyan-500/20">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">TypeScript quick start</h2>
        <pre class="bg-slate-950 rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto border border-slate-700 text-sm text-slate-300"><code>{tsSnippet}</code></pre>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-orange-500/20">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Rust quick start</h2>
        <pre class="bg-slate-950 rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto border border-slate-700 text-sm text-slate-300"><code>{rustSnippet}</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-teal-500/20">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Shared capabilities</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            <li>• Wallet creation, import, balance checks, and sends</li>
            <li>• Privacy and stealth-address workflows</li>
            <li>• Staking and validator interactions</li>
            <li>• Governance proposals and voting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Repo-backed examples</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            <li>• <code class="text-teal-300">sdks/sdk-typescript/examples/</code></li>
            <li>• <code class="text-teal-300">sdks/sdk-rust/examples/</code></li>
            <li>• Go example code in the module repo</li>
            <li>• Python and C# README-driven quick starts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-cyan-500/20">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Integration guidance</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            Pair an SDK with direct node RPC for low-level integrations, or combine it with the planned indexed API layer when you need explorer-style or analytics-style queries.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-950">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Pick the runtime that fits your stack</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
        Frontend app? TypeScript. Backend services? Rust, Go, Python, or C#. The repo already carries the language spread needed to support wallets, services, and protocol tooling.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/api" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-green-500 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-teal-500/30 transition-all duration-300">Explore API surfaces</a>
        <a href="/nodes" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white border border-white/20 font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-slate-900 transition-all duration-300">Deployment guides</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
